Subject: drm/v3d: Create function to update a set of GPU stats
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: da483d079bacceba6c999b4bb2b4c488ead12ed8
